### System paths

| Path | Owner | Purpose |
|------|-------|---------|
| `{{VAULT_PATH}}/guidelines/libs/<lib>-<version>.md` | @CodeWriter, @BugFixer | External library documentation cache |
| `{{VAULT_PATH}}/_templates/test-plan.md` | (template) | Template for @QA |
| `{{VAULT_PATH}}/_templates/test-cases.md` | (template) | Template for @TestRunner |
| `{{VAULT_PATH}}/_templates/bug-report.md` | (template) | Template for @BugFixer |
| `{{VAULT_PATH}}/_templates/spec.md` | (template) | Template for @Main |
| `{{VAULT_PATH}}/_templates/requirements.md` | (template) | Template for @Main |
| `{{VAULT_PATH}}/_templates/tech-debt.md` | (template) | Template for `tech-debt-record` skill |
| `{{VAULT_PATH}}/tech-debt/<module>/<slug>.md` | @CodeWriter, @BugFixer, @CodeReviewer, @SecurityReviewer, @TestExecutor | Open tech-debt entries (status: open\|in-progress) |
| `{{VAULT_PATH}}/tech-debt/<module>/done/<slug>.md` | @Main (via `/kit-techdebt`) | Closed entries (status: fixed\|wont-fix) |
| `{{VAULT_PATH}}/reference/<module>/spec/<feature>-trace.md` | @TraceabilityChecker | Traceability matrix per feature (AC/CC/endpoint → TC → test file → source) |
| `{{VAULT_PATH}}/reference/<module>/spec/<feature>-dod.md` | @DoDGate | Definition-of-Done verdict report — last gate before CLOSE |
| `{{VAULT_PATH}}/guidelines/<module>/reports/test-runs/<ISO>-stage-NN.md` | @TestExecutor | Independent run report per stage (build + unit + integration + TC mapping) |

